# .mirrorignore — paths excluded from the public mirror sync
#
# The public mirror (ForgeWireLabs/anvil) publishes the package itself: source,
# tests, fixtures, packaging metadata, docs, and licence. Release tooling that
# only makes sense inside the private monorepo is excluded.

# Mirror publication tooling: operates on the monorepo, not on a clone.
scripts/**

# The release checklist documents the private monorepo workflow. It hardcodes
# monorepo-local paths, refers to ForgeWire test trees that do not exist here,
# and drives scripts/sync_mirror.ps1 — which this file excludes, so publishing
# it would ship instructions for a script the reader does not have.
docs/releasing.md
